《'''BLEACH: Brave Souls'''》（{{jpn|j=BLEACH Brave Souls|kk=ブリーチ ブレイブソウル}}），是由[[KLab|KLab]]製作和營運的[[iOS|iOS]]及[[Android|Android]][[智慧手機系統|智能手機]][[格鬥遊戲|格鬥]][[動作遊戲|動作]][[冒險遊戲|冒險]][[抽卡遊戲|抽卡遊戲]]，為《[[BLEACH|BLEACH]]》系列遊戲之一<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hngn.com/articles/170067/20160115/bleach-brave-souls-mobile-game-now-available-ios-android.htm|title=‘Bleach: Brave Souls’ Mobile Game Now Available On iOS, Android|date=2016-01-15|website=Headlines & Global News|language=en|access-date=2020-01-17|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318092148/http://www.hngn.com/articles/170067/20160115/bleach-brave-souls-mobile-game-now-available-ios-android.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該遊戲於2017年10月突破全球2500萬次下載<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-01-06/bleach-cant-fear-your-own-world-novel-characters-to-appear-in-bleach-brave-souls-smartphone-game/.141673|title=Bleach: Can't Fear Your Own World Novel Characters to Appear in Bleach: Brave Souls Smartphone Game|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106210243/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-01-06/bleach-cant-fear-your-own-world-novel-characters-to-appear-in-bleach-brave-souls-smartphone-game/.141673|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年7月於亞洲地區上線，並突破5000萬次下載<ref>{{cite web|url=https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000373.000006348.html|title=『BLEACH Brave Souls』明日で5周年！全世界5000万ダウンロード達成！|publisher=PR TIMES|date=2020-07-22|access-date=2020-10-03|language=ja|archive-date=2020-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722110029/https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000373.000006348.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://dengekionline.com/articles/44600/|title=『ブレソル』5周年キャンペーン開催中。一護、白哉の5周年記念ver.が手に入るチャンス|publisher=電撃オンライン|date=2020-07-26|access-date=2020-10-03|language=ja|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007144122/https://dengekionline.com/articles/44600/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月27日，遊戲與原作[[久保帶人|久保帶人]]另一部漫畫《[[BURN_THE_WITCH|BURN THE WITCH]]》進行聯名合作活動<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bleach-bravesouls.com/tw/campaign/btw/|title=BURN THE WITCH聯名合作活動網站|accessdate=2020-10-03|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007144122/https://www.bleach-bravesouls.com/tw/campaign/btw/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://dengekionline.com/articles/51936/|title=『ブレソル』×『BURN THE WITCH』など、さまざまなコラボの最新情報を公開|publisher=電撃オンライン|date=2020-09-27|access-date=2020-10-03|language=ja|archive-date=2020-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201007144124/https://dengekionline.com/articles/51936/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

